Course Overview

This course prepares you for a system design interview by using a case study of DoorDash (a prepared food delivery system) and familiarizes you with the challenges you will encounter during the interview. You will begin by understanding the theory behind the system design interview t...

How You'll Learn

Faster than videos

Videos are holding you back. The average video tutorial is spoken at 150 words per minute, while you can read at 250. That‘s why our courses are text-based.

Progress you can show

Built-in assessments let you test your skills. Completion certificates let you show them off.
